      "blocks": {
        "text_Uaaxba": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "collapse": true,
            "title": "How can I preview my sign?",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_width": 50,
            "faq_answer": "<p>We’ve made it incredibly easy! Simply enter your custom dates, names, and select your milestones. Our system will generate a <strong>real-time digital rendering</strong> of your sign instantly. This allows you to see exactly how the 3D layered icons and text will look together, ensuring your story is perfect before we even start crafting it. No waiting for proofs—what you see is what we build!</p>",
            "page": "",
            "image_width": 465,
            "liquid": "",
            "html": "",
            "show_contact_form": false
          }
        },
        "text_TXhJbY": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "collapse": true,
            "title": "What material is used to make my wooden signs?",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_width": 50,
            "faq_answer": "<p><strong>Material:</strong> 5mm wood board + 5mm white acrylic sheet<br/><strong>Thickness:</strong> 10mm<br/><strong>Sizes:</strong> 10x27 inches and 12x30 inches.<br/><strong>Printing Process:</strong> UV printing<br/><strong>Processing Technology:</strong> Laser cutting<br/><strong>Accessories:</strong> Hemp rope<br/><strong>Packaging:</strong> Boxed</p>",
            "page": "",
            "image_width": 465,
            "liquid": "",
            "html": "",
            "show_contact_form": false
          }
        },
        "text_GhENPL": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "collapse": true,
            "title": "How do I track my package?",
            "icon": "none",
            "header_image_width": 50,
            "faq_answer": "<p>We use USPS, UPS, DHL or FedEx, the most reliable shipping carriers available. <strong>At any time, you can track your package to find out exactly where it is. </strong>And of course, we will send you the tracking link a few days after you purchase from us</p>",
            "page": "",
            "image_width": 465,
            "liquid": "",
            "html": "",
            "show_contact_form": false
          }
        },
